<HEADLINE>
<P>
HATE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 * Can anyone address this issue? I put forth 100% effort teaching the basics 
of algebra to my math classes. Recently, during my lesson, a student stood up, 
walked to the back of the room, and conversed with another student.I asked her 
to please return to her seat. She replied, "My friend has to explain it to me 
since you won't because I'm black." 
</P>
<P>
 Her classmates of all races told her she was way out of line. I knew there was 
no truth to her accusation. But I also know that our classrooms are full of 
students who come to school every day dragged down by this self-defeating 
attitude. 
</P>
