 Top-seeded Goran Ivanisevic survived a three-set battle with Canadian Greg 
Rusedski and won 5-7, 7-6 (7-5), 6-4 in the third round of the $1 million Super 
Seiko tournament in Tokyo. 
</P>
<P>
