No. 3 Stefan Edberg beat 13th-seeded Mark Woodforde, 6-4, 6-4 and fourth-seeded 
Todd Martin also advanced, beating fellow American Aaron Krickstein, 7-6 (7-0), 
0-6, 6-4. Names in the News 
</P>
