 The St. Louis Cardinals were expected to name Colorado Rocky front-office 
executive Walt Jocketty as the club's new general manager at a news conference 
today. He would replace Dal Maxvill, who was fired last month....Wilfredo 
Vasquez of Puerto Rico retained his WBA super bantamweight title in Paris with 
a unanimous decision over Juan Polo-Perez of Colombia. The judges scored it for 
Vasquez, 115-113, 116-111 and 116-112, in his eighth title defense 
