Metro; Part B; Page 1; Column 2 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
717 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
AERIAL SPRAYING IS A SUCCESS IN MEDFLY FIGHT, OFFICIALS SAY; AGRICULTURE: 
