<TEXT>
<P>
 Microwave Set for Kids: JusToys, a New York-based toy maker, has introduced 
the Micro-Bake Cake Set, which enables children to bake with a microwave 
without the danger of touching hot pans. 
</P>
<P>
 Using any packaged cake mix, children ages 8 and up can put the batter in the 
specially coated Micro-Bake pan, drop it into the Micro-Bake safety chamber and 
then place it in a home microwave oven. 
</P>
<P>
 After five minutes, the cake is done. But the safety lock on the safety 
chamber won't open until the pan is completely cool. 
</P>
<P>
 The Micro-Bake Cake Set also comes with an apron, measuring spoon and cup. It 
retails for about $19.99. 
